phase2.explanation:
🤖 **Common Hilt mistakes and fixes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| No scope | Add @Singleton |
| Wrong context | Use @ApplicationContext |
| Missing deps | Provide all deps |
| Circular | Refactor |
| No @Inject | Use constructor injection |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. Add scope
@Provides
@Singleton
fun provideDatabase(@ApplicationContext context: Context): AppDatabase

// 2. Use @ApplicationContext
fun provideRepository(@ApplicationContext context: Context): Repository

// 3. Provide all dependencies
@Provides
fun provideViewModel(
    repository: Repository
): MyViewModel

// 4. Use constructor injection
class MyClass @Inject constructor(
    private val dependency: Dependency
)

// 5. Add @HiltAndroidApp
@HiltAndroidApp
class MyApplication : Application()
```

